    <abstract>
      <t>This memo updates the IANA IPv6 Special-Purpose Address Registries to address issues raised by the definition of a global prefix. For completeness, this memo contains all the assignments made by RFC 6890 to the IANA Special-Purpose Address Registries. This memo obsoletes RFC 6890.</t>
